data.description: HOA ONLY $50/MONTH, NO LAND LEASE, YOU OWN YOUR DEEDED LOT INCLUDED IN THIS PRICE. This spacious home is a gem, featuring a fantastic Florida room right at the front, tucked away on a peaceful street. Inside, there's plenty of room to spread out, along with loads of storage space. 2022 SHINGLES ROOF, VERY NEW. It's being sold unfurnished, giving you the chance to add your own personal flair and make it truly yours. Located in Boynton Beach, South Florida, it's super convenient for hitting the beach, shopping, and catching flights at the airport. And here's the kicker: In Parry Village, you'll own the land outright--no pesky land leases here! Plus, the monthly HOA fee is just $50, making this deal the steal of Palm Beach County.
